high_descs: Turn around to stand in front of the sink.
Pick up the sharp knife from the drying rack on the left side of the sink.
Turn right, walk to the wall, turn right again, and continue straight to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the knife in the white mug on the shelf.
Pick up the mug with the knife in it from the shelf in the fridge.
Carry the mug and knife to the microwave cart, which is to your right.
Place the mug and knife on the microwave cart directly in front of the roll of paper towels.
anns.task_desc: Move a knife in a mug to the microwave cart.

high_descs: turn around, walk to face kitchen sink
pick up sharp knife with gold handle from drying area left of the sink
turn right, walk to face the fridge
open the fridge door, put the knife in the white mug on the top left shelf of fridge
pick up mug from fridge shelf, close the fridge door
walk to the right to face the microwave
put the mug on the counter to the left of the microwave between the salt and paper towels
anns.task_desc: put a chilled mug and knife near the microwave

high_descs: move to the sink to the right of you
pick up a knife from the sink
move to the fridge to the right
put the knife in a cup
pick up the cup from the fridge
move to the counter to the right of the fridge
put the cup on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put a cup on a counter with a knife.

high_descs: Turn right, go to the sink on the left.
Pick up the knife on the rack to the left of the sink.
Turn right, go towards the refrigerator on the right.
Open the refrigerator, put the knife in the white mug on the left.
Take the mug from the refrigerator, close the refrigerator.
Go in front of the counter with the microwave to the right.
Put the mug behind the pepper grinder and in front of the paper towel roll on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a knife on a counter.

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk until you are facing the left side of the sink
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle.
Turn to your right and walk until you hit the wall then turn right again and stand in front of the fridge so you are facing it.
Open the fridge and put the knife in the white mug to the left of the green cup.
Retrieve the cup and knife on the shelf and close the door.
Turn to your right and walk a couple steps so your are by the microwave and then face it.
Put down the mug to the left of the microwave between the pepper grinder and paper towels.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup with  a knife in it beside the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the oven but make a right at the kitchen sink.
Pick up the knife next to the sink.
Turn right, walk towards the wall, and turn left towards the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the knife in the white cup.
Remove the white cup with the knife from the fridge.
Turn right and walk towards the microwave on the left.
Place the cup behind the pepper shaker.
anns.task_desc: Place the white cup with a knife behind the pepper shaker.
